Kita tinggal dua hari lagi.

411
00:26:28,351 --> 00:26:33,314
Makin siap musuh,
makin kejam aku harus bertindak.

412
00:26:33,481 --> 00:26:34,733
Meski bukan keinginanku,

413
00:26:34,858 --> 00:26:36,317
