George bilang
dia menghampirinya.

428
00:27:30,205 --> 00:27:32,957
Dia yang menghampirinya, bukan?

429
00:27:48,681 --> 00:27:50,600
Kupikir aku mampir
untuk memperkenalkan diri.

430
00:27:50,725 --> 00:27:52,435
Bernard Montgomery.

431
00:27:53,394 --> 00:27:55,146
Oh, ya.

432
00:27:56,220 --> 00:27:58,848
Halo. James Stagg.

433
00:27:59,705 --> 00:28:01,165
