Tidak, Pak.

447
00:28:54,247 --> 00:28:55,707
Astaga.

448
00:28:55,915 --> 00:28:57,083
Baiklah.

449
00:28:57,208 --> 00:28:58,459
Kita siap berangkat?

450
00:28:58,543 --> 00:28:59,752
Ke mana?

451
